channel.title: RSPSR - Runescape Private Server Reviews
channel.description:
Hello guys,
I'm here to tell you guys about a new website that one of my friends has opened up called RSPSR, its a brand new website which is all about funnily enough writing reviews on private servers. The website is sourly based on what the players thoughts are on the server(s) they play. So people like you can turn to the site and look for a server see a review and think that could be a server they would like to play. If you are interested then please come and visit the site and just write a review on what server you play. Will only take 2 minutes and will be a great help to other players.
Thanks for reading guys and i hope you join www.google.com/imgay
